WEBVTT

23:59:37.870 --> 23:59:44.210
♫ We... are the crystal gems,
we'll always save the day, ♫

23:59:44.220 --> 23:59:48.880
♫ And if you think we can't,
we'll always find a way, ♫

23:59:49.340 --> 23:59:54.250
♫ That's why the people
of this world believe in, ♫

23:59:54.780 --> 23:59:59.781
♫ Garnet, Amethyst, and
Pearl... and Steven! ♫

00:00.160 --> 00:03.140
Episode 2b
"Together Breakfast"

00:07.920 --> 00:08.750
Everyone's out.

00:09.500 --> 00:10.900
Guess I'm making us breakfast.

00:12.000 --> 00:18.074
